profile:
We build wooden garden sheds, bunkies, pub sheds and storage sheds that can be installed by our experienced team in a day or constructe­d as a do it yourself kit that you build yourself. With unparalleled personal service, experienced builders, state of the art power tools and a professional workshop we ensure that we are always a cut above the rest. We serve southern Ontario, the greater Toronto area and cottage country. Our professional customer service and experienced team will ensure to help you design and build the appropriate shed for your particular needs.

DIY Do It Yourself Shed Kit Includes:

- Floor (entirely precut & ready to assemble)
- 1 front wall, 1 back wall & 2 side walls (all walls ship fully prebuilt & assembled with doors installed)
- Roof (trusses prebuilt and preassembled; roof panels are all precut and ready to assemble)
- Wooden 60″ double doors (two 30″ wide single doors that open outwards) or with our 6 ft. or smaller front walls we provide one single wooden 36″ door)
- All components are delivered precut and preassembled with instructions to ensure a hassle free construction. Our shed kits come complete with all four walls fully prebuilt, all wood precut with clear markings and hardware included (roofing nails & Tapcons if needed are not supplied).
products: Wooden Sheds: Gable, Cottage Workshop, Barn, Single Slope, Bunkie & Pub Sheds.
services: Please visit our website at www.shedinaday.com to learn more and to request a quote with pricing.
name: Shed In A Day

profile: Future Buildings is a large manufacturer and distributor of prefabricated steel buildings. The company was founded in 1981. Its headquarters is based in Markham, Ontario, Canada. Future Buildings offers the following types steel buildings: Garage, Workshop, Storage, Agricultural, and Commercial. An estimate is provided on a free of charge basis. The company also offers a free brochure. All buildings come in kit form with manuals. They are made from Galvalume Plus Steel. Future Buildings provides a 30 year rust perforation warranty. Customer assistance is provided by phone and by e-mail.

profile:
Miladian Homes was founded in 2010, but our team has been doing custom carpentry and building high quality decks, fences, pergolas, and cabanas for over 20 years. Taking care of our customers has always been our top priority. Our goal is to do great work with every project, while also keeping our job sites clean, showing respect for our customers' properties, and keeping our projects on schedule and on budget.

If you're looking to improve your deck or backyard, we're happy to talk to you. Give us a call any time!

profile:
TORO Steel Buildings is a  supplier of pre engineered steel buildings – all uses, all sizes, all finishes. Consumers and contractors come to us because we develop fast, efficient and affordable metal building solutions.

From a basic backyard storage shed to a more complex commercial steel building project, we have the expertise to deliver your new building on-time and on budget. The engineering and service team at Toro Steel Buildings is committed to saving you time and money by providing you with the best-quality steel building – at the best possible price. We have spent decades establishing the service and value formula that we have today which promises our customers that every dollar and minute is well spent.
